data.title: Steve 'n' Seagulls
data.meta_description: Steve 'n' Seagulls at G Livelab, Helsinki. Buy your official ticket in advance!
data.text:
Steve ’n’ Seagulls, formed in 2010, is a Finnish band known for their diverse musical style blending newgrass, country, rock, and bluegrass. Their extensive instrument repertoire includes banjo, mandolin, drums, double bass, accordion, guitar, flute, and more. Initially gaining popularity with rock and metal classics reinterpretations, the band has showcased their original work on their latest albums. Steve ’n’ Seagulls has captivated audiences with energetic live performances, touring extensively worldwide.

The concert is open to people of all ages.
